The paper deals with the optimization of streaming delivery techniques for 360° videos, which involves analyzing user behavior and designing systems to reduce bandwidth costs and improve playback experiences. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Multimedia (cs.MM), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
